2638 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/aisha-ignorance-faults\/","url_meta":{"origin":35278,"position":2},"title":"Aisha on Ignorance: People fast to criticize what they do not know","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abbad ibn Abdullah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her said, \u201cHow quick are people to fault what they have no knowledge about!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 973 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0651\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0639\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3449,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/28\/all-people-children-adam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35278,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adam: All people are the children of Adam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has removed from you the pride of the time of ignorance with its boasting of\u00a0ancestors. Verily, one is only a\u00a0righteous\u00a0believer or a miserable sinner. All of the people are\u00a0the children of Adam, and Adam was created\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/18\/good-deeds-before-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35278,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Good deeds before conversion to Islam rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hakim ibn Hizam reported: He said to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhat do you think of the acts of worship I did in the time of ignorance. Will I get anything from them?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou have embraced Islam with the good you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15620,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/hajj-markets-jahiliyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35278,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Trading during pilgrimage season","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Dhul al-Majaz, 'Ukazha, and Matjar were markets people attended in the time of ignorance. When Islam came, the companions disliked that during the Hajj season until the verse was revealed, \u201cThere is no blame on you for seeking the bounty of your Lord during this journey.\" (2:198)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35278","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=35278"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35278\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=35278"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=35278"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=35278"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}